   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00217"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168934" type="place">IX Franckgasse 1</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00218"/><date>27. VII.</date></dateline><salute>lieber Arthur</salute></opener><p>bitte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o lieb und<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chicken an <rs ref="#pmb10765" type="person">Poldy</rs>
                  (<rs ref="#pmb34314" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Villa Andrian</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb34401" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Alt-Aussee</hi></rs>) möglich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t bald ein <hi rend="underline" n="1">Buch</hi> wo Symptome
               gewöhnlicher Neura<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>thenie drin<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tehen, damit er nervö<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e Beklemmungen u. dgl. als<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>olche erkennen kann.</p><p>Bin wohl und hätte gern Nachricht von Ihnen, bis <date>5<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi> Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date> hierher.</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr<lb/><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
